Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:25.37,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}e{\3c&H000000&\blur4.5} tenta te macucar complawards,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:31.17,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Mesmo que o mundo inteiro não acredite em você
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:36.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}E coloque uma coroa de espinhos em sua cabeça
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:42.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Posso tomar seu lado, e só o seu
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:48.14,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Eu conheço a sua dor e solidão
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.15,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5}Então, tudo que me completa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:57.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,580)\3c&H000000&}Eu vou te dar isso agora
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:37.49,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Eu{\3c&H000000&}caminho{\3c&H000000&}nos{\3c&H000000&}sagazes{\3c&H000000&}ayou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.50,0:02:05.02,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&}Eu{\3c&H000000&}não{\3c&H000000&}conheço{\3c&H000000&}quantas{\3c&H000000&}coisas{\3c&H000000&}felizes{\3c&H000000&}existem
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:11.65,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)}{\3c&H000000&}Eu{\3c&H000000&}criaria{\3c&H000000&}algo{\3c&H000000&}futurista
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.15,0:02:19.74,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&}Darka{\3c&H000000&}diz{\3c&H000000&}que{\3c&H000000&}isso{\3c&H000000&}é{\3c&H000000&}uma{\3c&H000000&}mentira
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.86,0:02:25.37,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Mesmo com palavras que ferem o coração
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:31.17,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Sem que o mundo acredite em você
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:36.92,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Mesmo usando a coroa de espinhos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:42.68,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Eu serei seu único companheiro
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:48.14,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Kimi no itami mo kodoku mo shitte iru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:57.90,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,580)\3c&H000000&}Agora eu te dedico
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.55,0:14:38.64,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur3}Nunca mais serei amado por você
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:45.15,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur3}Nem precisado de você novamente
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:54.20,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur3}Então, tudo que me completa
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:15:02.17,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur3}Você sempre faz isso, me deixa com raiva
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:08.63,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur3}E depois me faz chorar no final
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.05,0:15:15.14,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur3}Mas quando você disse "Me desculpa" depois,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.84,0:15:21.76,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu sempre amei a expressão no seu rosto
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.59,0:15:59.18,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sim, me abrace o mais forte que puder e não solte
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:05.31,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu quero estar nos seus braços
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:23.26,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vamos dormir com as testas encostadas
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.27,0:17:00.77,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Você sempre faz isso, me deixando com raiva
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:07.08,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}E depois me fazendo chorar no fim
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:13.84,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fad(200,200)\blur3}Mas quando você disse "Me desculpa" depois,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.84,0:17:20.05,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu sempre amei a expressão no seu rosto
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:58.33,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sim, me abrace forte quanto puder e não solte
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:04.93,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Eu quero estar nos seus braços
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:21.53,Other songs,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Vamos dormir com as testas encostadas
